  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"BENEFIT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"If workers' compensation benefits are available for a bodily injury, coverage under this part II is not provided."&lt;SEP&gt;"Workers' compensation benefits are available for bodily injury sustained by a person while occupying or struck by a vehicle owned by the policyholder or furnished for regular use, excluding a covered auto for which this coverage has been purchased."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-9d1b4fcafc6c7d7efe5c322ad9bd33fd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6ea57b3201f9d42edca3669635573a74</data>
