</node>
<node id="&quot;ACCIDENT&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"An accident is a situation requiring specific duties to be fulfilled."&lt;SEP&gt;"An accident is an event that results in damage to a covered vehicle or its parts."&lt;SEP&gt;"An accident is an unforeseen event that leads to legal responsibility for damages."&lt;SEP&gt;"An accident is an unforeseen event that results in bodily injury or property damage for which an insured person may be held legally responsible."&lt;SEP&gt;"An accident refers to an incident resulting in bodily injury to an insured person, which may trigger coverage under the policy."&lt;SEP&gt;"An incident causing injury."&lt;SEP&gt;"An incident resulting in bodily injury, which may trigger coverage."&lt;SEP&gt;"An unexpected event causing bodily injury, which must be linked to the uninsured motor vehicle."&lt;SEP&gt;"An unexpected incident causing damage to property, which may trigger insurance claims."&lt;SEP&gt;"An unforeseen incident that may trigger a claim."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-8a3491a1885e53367b27b22e975a6fbb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-38c1857f7eddbd65f102ae432a80d4ea&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d016c8b9bbaa3c5bae4936f9d698a1c1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9cd680372852b670779cd9ab038f278e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ed4d5b68d5d2c5cb43c341277461c05d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d2d8f56664f7ecfe69d0c03f4f89540c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9d1b4fcafc6c7d7efe5c322ad9bd33fd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-55b66238ae6adb6999a975e6b7f7834c</data>
</node>
