  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"ACTION"</data>
  <data key="d4">"Exiting a vehicle is part of the definition of occupying."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-3bb98005a1307a094baa1b3869aeea6c</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;INSURANCE APPLICATION&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"DOCUMENT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"A document submitted by the insured to apply for insurance coverage, which becomes part of the policy contract."&lt;SEP&gt;"The insurance application is incorporated into the policy as part of the contract."&lt;SEP&gt;"The insurance application is part of the policy and contains information provided by the applicant."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-20da18c34f7340c40297873edec25e72&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2e3e05ae8cb995bb756587490f5512f4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e2c04092b664c68f63780007564ef50d</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;DEPRECIATION&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"Depreciation accounts for the loss of value over time, and may reduce the payment for damaged property based on its age and condition."&lt;SEP&gt;"Depreciation is a factor considered when adjusting the cost to repair or replace damaged property."&lt;SEP&gt;"The reduction in value of an asset over time due to age, wear, or obsolescence."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-98ea72d43f9051dc6899f8d6aafcd9a5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8a3491a1885e53367b27b22e975a6fbb</data>
</node>
