</node>
<node id="&quot;BREAKAGE OF GLASS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"Breakage of glass not caused by collision is a covered loss."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-ed4d5b68d5d2c5cb43c341277461c05d</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;PERSONAL VEHICLE SHARING PROGRAM&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"PROGRAM"</data>
  <data key="d4">"A personal vehicle sharing program involves the temporary exchange of vehicle use for compensation, which may trigger exclusions unless operated by the insured, a relative, or a rated resident."&lt;SEP&gt;"A personal vehicle sharing program is a system or process operated by a business, organization, network, group, or individual that facilitates the sharing of private passenger motor vehicles for use by individuals, businesses, or other entities."&lt;SEP&gt;"A program involving temporary vehicle sharing for compensation."&lt;SEP&gt;"A program involving temporary vehicle sharing."&lt;SEP&gt;"A program where a vehicle is shared with others for compensation, which triggers the exclusion when a covered auto is used in such a program."&lt;SEP&gt;"A program where individuals share personal vehicles for compensation."&lt;SEP&gt;"A program where individuals share personal vehicles with others for non-commercial purposes."&lt;SEP&gt;"Use of a covered auto in a personal vehicle sharing program is not covered."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-245fa605e8e023a6acdcf8c36c35930e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3bb98005a1307a094baa1b3869aeea6c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9cd680372852b670779cd9ab038f278e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9fee7a00b84094770f04dcfe86a29e3a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9d1b4fcafc6c7d7efe5c322ad9bd33fd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cfb324337b8eb7e557e96d41d0a59527</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;ENDORSEMENTS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"DOCUMENT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"Amendments or additions to the policy that modify coverage terms, issued by the insurer."&lt;SEP&gt;"Endorsements are additions or modifications to the policy issued by the insurer."&lt;SEP&gt;"Endorsements are amendments to the policy that modify its terms."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-20da18c34f7340c40297873edec25e72&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2e3e05ae8cb995bb756587490f5512f4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e2c04092b664c68f63780007564ef50d</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;BETTERMENT&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"Betterment refers to improvements beyond the original condition and is considered when adjusting repair or replacement costs."&lt;SEP&gt;"Betterment refers to the improvement in value or condition of a repaired item beyond its original state, which may reduce the insurer's payment."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-98ea72d43f9051dc6899f8d6aafcd9a5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8a3491a1885e53367b27b22e975a6fbb</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;FRAUDULENT CONDUCT&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"ACTION"</data>
  <data key="d4">"Any dishonest or deceptive behavior related to a loss."&lt;SEP&gt;"Intentional deception to gain an unfair advantage."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-245fa605e8e023a6acdcf8c36c35930e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-38c1857f7eddbd65f102ae432a80d4ea</data>
</node>
