  <data key="d4">"Physical or emotional harm to a person."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-8a3491a1885e53367b27b22e975a6fbb</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;DEDUCTIBLE AMOUNT&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"AMOUNT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"The amount the policyholder pays before insurance kicks in."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-8a3491a1885e53367b27b22e975a6fbb</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;BODILY INJURY&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"Bodily injury is a type of claim that may be excluded under this policy under specific conditions."&lt;SEP&gt;"Bodily injury is a type of damage covered under the policy."&lt;SEP&gt;"Bodily injury is a type of damage for which the insured may be legally responsible and for which the insurer will pay damages."&lt;SEP&gt;"Bodily injury refers to bodily harm, sickness, or disease, including death resulting from such harm, sickness, or disease."&lt;SEP&gt;"Bodily injury refers to physical harm sustained by a person while occupying or struck by a vehicle, which may or may not be covered under this policy depending on circumstances."&lt;SEP&gt;"Injury to a person resulting from a motor vehicle accident, covered under liability limits."&lt;SEP&gt;"Physical harm or injury to a person, which is excluded if caused by the use of a non-covered vehicle without proper permission."&lt;SEP&gt;"Physical harm or injury to a person."&lt;SEP&gt;"Physical harm or injury to a person; coverage is excluded under certain conditions."&lt;SEP&gt;"Physical harm sustained by an insured person that is covered under this policy."&lt;SEP&gt;"Physical harm sustained by the insured, a relative, or a rated resident."&lt;SEP&gt;"Physical harm sustained in a motor vehicle accident, which triggers coverage under Part II."&lt;SEP&gt;"Physical harm to a person resulting from an accident, which triggers coverage and payment considerations."&lt;SEP&gt;"Physical harm to a person, which may be covered under the policy."&lt;SEP&gt;"Physical harm to a person."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-cc674f73d7a5cb327513cff560eedac9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8a3491a1885e53367b27b22e975a6fbb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3bb98005a1307a094baa1b3869aeea6c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8918d81dfdf6055a12c8c1d621356d08&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d016c8b9bbaa3c5bae4936f9d698a1c1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fb0aea7627d6cab63c56603774515efc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9fee7a00b84094770f04dcfe86a29e3a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cfb324337b8eb7e557e96d41d0a59527&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6ea57b3201f9d42edca3669635573a74&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d2d8f56664f7ecfe69d0c03f4f89540c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9d1b4fcafc6c7d7efe5c322ad9bd33fd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-55b66238ae6adb6999a975e6b7f7834c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-798fdf9e8255810d437349cea720f315</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;TRANSPORTATION EXPENSES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"FINANCIAL CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"Costs incurred for alternative transportation due to vehicle unavailability."&lt;SEP&gt;"Reasonable transportation expenses are covered if a covered auto is stolen."&lt;SEP&gt;"Transportation expenses are not covered if Rental Reimbursement Coverage is in place."&lt;SEP&gt;"Transportation expenses require written proof for reimbursement."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-ed4d5b68d5d2c5cb43c341277461c05d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9ac858e839dd324c4b80701da2b87bd7</data>
</node>
