  <data key="d4">"A business can operate a personal vehicle sharing program."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-3bb98005a1307a094baa1b3869aeea6c</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;AGREEMENTS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"The mutual understandings and commitments between the insured and the insurer as defined in the policy."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-20da18c34f7340c40297873edec25e72</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;PHYSICAL CONDITION&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"The current state of the damaged property, including wear and tear, which affects the repair cost and payment amount."&lt;SEP&gt;"The physical condition of property is a factor in determining repair or replacement cost adjustments."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-98ea72d43f9051dc6899f8d6aafcd9a5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8a3491a1885e53367b27b22e975a6fbb</data>
</node>
