<node id="&quot;30 DAYS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"TIME PERIOD"</data>
  <data key="d4">"For theft of a rented non-owned auto, coverage ends 30 days after loss of use begins."&lt;SEP&gt;"The deadline for notifying the insurer of ownership of an additional auto."&lt;SEP&gt;"The deadline within which each party must appoint an appraiser after a demand for appraisal."&lt;SEP&gt;"The deadline within which the two arbitrators must agree on a third arbitrator."&lt;SEP&gt;"The maximum duration for which rental reimbursement coverage applies."&lt;SEP&gt;"The policyholder must notify the insurer within 30 days of becoming the owner of an additional auto."&lt;SEP&gt;"The time limit for notifying the insurer after becoming the owner of an additional auto is 30 days."</data>
