  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"SECTION"</data>
  <data key="d4">"A section of the insurance policy that contains specific coverage details."&lt;SEP&gt;"Part IV is a section of the insurance policy that defines coverage terms."&lt;SEP&gt;"Part IV is a section of the insurance policy that includes coverage for damage to a vehicle, which may be added to the replacement auto upon notification."&lt;SEP&gt;"Part IV refers to the section of the insurance policy that governs coverage for loss to autos, including custom parts and equipment."&lt;SEP&gt;"The section of the insurance policy that governs coverage for loss to autos, including custom parts and equipment."</data>
