<node id="&quot;RIDE-SHARING ACTIVITY&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"ACTIVITY"</data>
  <data key="d4">"A service where individuals share rides, typically through a digital platform, to reduce transportation costs."&lt;SEP&gt;"Ride-sharing activities using a covered auto are excluded from coverage."&lt;SEP&gt;"Ride-sharing activities, such as those conducted via apps, are excluded from coverage."&lt;SEP&gt;"Ride-sharing activity is the use of a vehicle to transport persons or property via a transportation network company, starting from login/sign-in to logout/sign-off, regardless of whether a passenger or delivery assignment is accepted."&lt;SEP&gt;"Ride-sharing, such as using a vehicle to transport others for compensation, is excluded."&lt;SEP&gt;"The use of a vehicle to transport passengers for compensation, such as through apps like Uber or Lyft."&lt;SEP&gt;"Use of a covered auto for ride-sharing is not covered."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-cc674f73d7a5cb327513cff560eedac9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-245fa605e8e023a6acdcf8c36c35930e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d016c8b9bbaa3c5bae4936f9d698a1c1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8918d81dfdf6055a12c8c1d621356d08&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9cd680372852b670779cd9ab038f278e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6ea57b3201f9d42edca3669635573a74&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-55b66238ae6adb6999a975e6b7f7834c</data>
