<node id="&quot;FRAUD&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"Fraud is a prohibited act that nullifies lienholder protection."&lt;SEP&gt;"Fraudulent behavior related to policy procurement, continuation, change, or renewal is a valid reason for cancellation."&lt;SEP&gt;"Intentional deception to gain unfair advantage."&lt;SEP&gt;"Intentional deception to gain unfair or unlawful advantage."&lt;SEP&gt;"Intentional deception to secure unfair or unlawful gain, which may void the policy."</data>
