  <data key="d4">"Payments reduced by other payments."&lt;SEP&gt;"Payments under Medical Payments Coverage are reduced by any amounts paid under other parts of the policy, such as Liability To Others or Uninsured/Underinsured Motorist Coverage."&lt;SEP&gt;"Payments under Medical Payments Coverage are reduced by any amounts paid under other policy sections."&lt;SEP&gt;"Payments under one section are reduced by payments under another."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-9d1b4fcafc6c7d7efe5c322ad9bd33fd</data>
