</node>
<node id="&quot;MEDICAL SERVICES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"SERVICE"</data>
  <data key="d4">"Healthcare provided after an accident, subject to reasonableness review."&lt;SEP&gt;"Healthcare services required due to bodily injury from a motor vehicle accident."&lt;SEP&gt;"Medical services are a core component of coverage under this part II, and their necessity is a determining factor."&lt;SEP&gt;"Medical services are the healthcare services that an insured person may incur, which could be deemed unreasonable or unnecessary."&lt;SEP&gt;"Medical services are treatments or care provided to an insured person after an injury, which may be excluded if deemed unreasonable or unnecessary."&lt;SEP&gt;"Medical services include a broad range of healthcare services such as medical, surgical, dental, x-ray, ambulance, hospital, professional nursing, and funeral services, as well as costs for eyeglasses, hearing aids, pharmaceuticals, orthopedics, and prosthetic devices."&lt;SEP&gt;"Treatments or care provided to an injured person, which may be covered if deemed reasonable and necessary."&lt;SEP&gt;"Treatments provided to injured persons."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-9d1b4fcafc6c7d7efe5c322ad9bd33fd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6ea57b3201f9d42edca3669635573a74&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-798fdf9e8255810d437349cea720f315&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d2d8f56664f7ecfe69d0c03f4f89540c</data>
</node>
