<node id="&quot;YOU&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"PERSON"</data>
  <data key="d4">"'You' refers to a person named as an insured on the declarations page."&lt;SEP&gt;"'You' refers to the policyholder or primary insured individual."&lt;SEP&gt;"'You' refers to the policyholder, who assumes liability under contracts or agreements that are not covered."&lt;SEP&gt;"'You' refers to the policyholder, who is considered an insured person under this policy for accidents related to the ownership, maintenance, or use of an auto or trailer."&lt;SEP&gt;"The insured is a party with whom the insurer may settle a loss."&lt;SEP&gt;"The policyholder is a person whose intentional or willful act may void coverage."&lt;SEP&gt;"The policyholder is exempt from the auto business exclusion when using a covered auto."&lt;SEP&gt;"The policyholder or insured individual who enters into the agreement with the insurer."&lt;SEP&gt;"The policyholder or insured individual."&lt;SEP&gt;"The policyholder or their representative must accept the renewal offer."&lt;SEP&gt;"The policyholder responsible for reporting changes to the insurer."&lt;SEP&gt;"The policyholder responsible for verifying and updating information related to the policy."&lt;SEP&gt;"The policyholder who may obtain a driver's license or operator's permit."&lt;SEP&gt;"The policyholder who provides information used to determine the premium."&lt;SEP&gt;"The policyholder whose license or permit status must be reported."&lt;SEP&gt;"The policyholder, referred to as 'you' in the text."&lt;SEP&gt;"The policyholder, who is considered an insured person."&lt;SEP&gt;"The policyholder, who is responsible for additional charges if the vehicle is towed elsewhere."&lt;SEP&gt;"The policyholder."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-20da18c34f7340c40297873edec25e72&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cc674f73d7a5cb327513cff560eedac9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-245fa605e8e023a6acdcf8c36c35930e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-98ea72d43f9051dc6899f8d6aafcd9a5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-708cd65887876aa076b711ced7a4979e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8918d81dfdf6055a12c8c1d621356d08&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d016c8b9bbaa3c5bae4936f9d698a1c1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9cd680372852b670779cd9ab038f278e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9fee7a00b84094770f04dcfe86a29e3a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6ea57b3201f9d42edca3669635573a74&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d2d8f56664f7ecfe69d0c03f4f89540c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-33661b5c04aa1251a71c27b799dfbfc2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-55b66238ae6adb6999a975e6b7f7834c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f67c7ff74642b092b6581278092146d7</data>
