  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"PERSON"</data>
  <data key="d4">"A family member of the insured person."&lt;SEP&gt;"A family member of the insured."&lt;SEP&gt;"A family member of the named insured."&lt;SEP&gt;"A family member of the policyholder who may be covered under the policy."&lt;SEP&gt;"A family member of the policyholder who may incur veterinary expenses for a pet."&lt;SEP&gt;"A family member of the policyholder who may obtain a driver's license or operator's permit."&lt;SEP&gt;"A family member of the policyholder, referred to as 'a relative'."&lt;SEP&gt;"A family member of the policyholder, who is considered an insured person."&lt;SEP&gt;"A family member of the policyholder."&lt;SEP&gt;"A family member whose license or permit status must be reported."&lt;SEP&gt;"A rated resident is not a relative of the policyholder."&lt;SEP&gt;"A relative is a family member of the insured person, included under the definition of 'Insured person'."&lt;SEP&gt;"A relative is a family member of the policyholder who may be covered under the policy, including those who own or use vehicles furnished for their regular use."&lt;SEP&gt;"A relative is a person related by blood, marriage, or adoption to the policyholder and is considered an insured person under this policy."&lt;SEP&gt;"A relative is a person residing in the same household as the policyholder, related by blood, marriage, or adoption, and includes a ward, stepchild, or foster child. Unmarried dependent children temporarily away from home qualify as relatives if they intend to return."&lt;SEP&gt;"A relative is defined as someone who qualifies under the condition of intending to continue residing in the household, including unmarried dependent children temporarily away from home."&lt;SEP&gt;"A relative is excluded from the transfer that triggers termination."&lt;SEP&gt;"A relative is exempt from the auto business exclusion when using a covered auto."&lt;SEP&gt;"A relative is someone related by blood, marriage, or adoption, and their regular use of a vehicle not covered under the policy is excluded unless the vehicle is maintained or used by the insured."&lt;SEP&gt;"A relative must be convicted or plead guilty to a criminal act or omission for exclusion to apply."&lt;SEP&gt;"A relative of the insured may be involved in illegal activities that trigger exclusion."&lt;SEP&gt;"A relative of the policyholder is a person whose intentional or willful act may void coverage."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-20da18c34f7340c40297873edec25e72&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cc674f73d7a5cb327513cff560eedac9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-245fa605e8e023a6acdcf8c36c35930e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3bb98005a1307a094baa1b3869aeea6c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8918d81dfdf6055a12c8c1d621356d08&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d016c8b9bbaa3c5bae4936f9d698a1c1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9cd680372852b670779cd9ab038f278e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9fee7a00b84094770f04dcfe86a29e3a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6ea57b3201f9d42edca3669635573a74&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9d1b4fcafc6c7d7efe5c322ad9bd33fd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d2d8f56664f7ecfe69d0c03f4f89540c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-33661b5c04aa1251a71c27b799dfbfc2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ba971e62cee92a6aaf201ec7e51cf087&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-55b66238ae6adb6999a975e6b7f7834c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cfb324337b8eb7e557e96d41d0a59527&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f67c7ff74642b092b6581278092146d7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f25ed079d4b7f6c7141fd78422f7f726</data>
</node>
