  <data key="d3">"TIME PERIOD"</data>
  <data key="d4">"Notice is mailed more than 33 days before the end of the policy period."&lt;SEP&gt;"The duration of the policy, which extends until its end for certain parties after the named insured's death."&lt;SEP&gt;"The duration of the policy."&lt;SEP&gt;"The policy applies only to events occurring during the policy period shown on the declarations page."&lt;SEP&gt;"The time frame during which the insurance policy is active."&lt;SEP&gt;"The time frame during which the policy is in effect."&lt;SEP&gt;"The time frame of the policy."&lt;SEP&gt;"The time period during which the policy is in effect."</data>
