  <data key="d2">chunk-f67c7ff74642b092b6581278092146d7</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;PART II-MEDICAL PAYMENTS COVERAGE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"POLICY SECTION"</data>
  <data key="d4">"Part II provides coverage for medical expenses incurred due to a motor vehicle accident, regardless of fault."&lt;SEP&gt;"Part II provides medical payments to insured persons for injuries sustained in an accident, subject to limits and exclusions."&lt;SEP&gt;"This part covers medical payments and triggers reimbursement obligations."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-9d1b4fcafc6c7d7efe5c322ad9bd33fd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-798fdf9e8255810d437349cea720f315&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f67c7ff74642b092b6581278092146d7</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;LOSS PAYABLE CLAUSE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"CLAUSE"</data>
  <data key="d4">"A clause in the policy that specifies who is entitled to receive payment in the event of a loss."&lt;SEP&gt;"A clause specifying who receives payment in case of loss."&lt;SEP&gt;"A clause specifying who will receive the insurance payment in the event of a loss."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-e4f63404276c60a3d82c899176c55043&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2e3e05ae8cb995bb756587490f5512f4</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;LOSS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"A loss is an incident that occurs at a specific time, and the spouse's eligibility depends on household residency at that time."&lt;SEP&gt;"A negative outcome resulting in financial or physical damage."&lt;SEP&gt;"An incident causing damage to property, such as a vehicle or custom parts, that triggers insurance coverage."&lt;SEP&gt;"An incident that results in damage or loss of a covered auto."&lt;SEP&gt;"Loss refers to damage, destruction, or financial harm to insured property that may or may not be covered under the policy."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-8a3491a1885e53367b27b22e975a6fbb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-38c1857f7eddbd65f102ae432a80d4ea&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9ac858e839dd324c4b80701da2b87bd7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-708cd65887876aa076b711ced7a4979e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-55b66238ae6adb6999a975e6b7f7834c</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;15 DAYS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"TIME PERIOD"</data>
  <data key="d4">"A 15-day notice period is required if cancellation is due to nonpayment of premium."&lt;SEP&gt;"The deadline within which appraisers must agree on an umpire; otherwise, a court may intervene."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-708cd65887876aa076b711ced7a4979e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f25ed079d4b7f6c7141fd78422f7f726</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;PERSON&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"PERSON"</data>
  <data key="d4">"An individual who may receive a payment under Part I of the policy."&lt;SEP&gt;"An individual who sustained bodily injury."&lt;SEP&gt;"An individual who sustains bodily injury while using or occupying a vehicle."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-cc674f73d7a5cb327513cff560eedac9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9fee7a00b84094770f04dcfe86a29e3a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cfb324337b8eb7e557e96d41d0a59527</data>
</node>
