</node>
<node id="&quot;CANCELLATION&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"PROCESS"</data>
  <data key="d4">"Any named insured may cancel the policy."&lt;SEP&gt;"Cancellation may occur due to nonpayment of premium, and a cancellation fee is charged only during the initial policy period."&lt;SEP&gt;"Termination of the policy before expiration."&lt;SEP&gt;"The cancellation can be initiated by calling or writing the insurer and stating a future effective date."&lt;SEP&gt;"The termination of the policy before its end."&lt;SEP&gt;"The termination of the policy before its expiration date."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-2e3e05ae8cb995bb756587490f5512f4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-69d3b921f75f85252f4c9cdeaa3141bb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-38c1857f7eddbd65f102ae432a80d4ea&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f67c7ff74642b092b6581278092146d7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f25ed079d4b7f6c7141fd78422f7f726</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;DAMAGES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"Damages include compensation for bodily injury and property damage resulting from an accident."&lt;SEP&gt;"Damages refer to losses or harm to property, and duplicate recovery for the same elements is prohibited."&lt;SEP&gt;"Financial losses resulting from an incident covered by the policy."&lt;SEP&gt;"The amount of damages is determined using these systems."&lt;SEP&gt;"The amount of damages sustained by the insured person is determined by a binding decision of two arbitrators."&lt;SEP&gt;"The compensation for harm or loss resulting from an accident, which cannot be duplicated."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-20da18c34f7340c40297873edec25e72&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-38c1857f7eddbd65f102ae432a80d4ea&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-98ea72d43f9051dc6899f8d6aafcd9a5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ed4d5b68d5d2c5cb43c341277461c05d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-55b66238ae6adb6999a975e6b7f7834c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-798fdf9e8255810d437349cea720f315</data>
</node>
