</node>
<node id="&quot;DUPLICATE PAYMENTS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"No individual can receive more than one payment for the same damages, preventing overcompensation."&lt;SEP&gt;"No individual may receive duplicate payments under the policy for the same damages, ensuring that benefits are not double-counted."&lt;SEP&gt;"Payments made more than once for the same damage or loss, which are prohibited under the policy."&lt;SEP&gt;"Payments made more than once for the same damages, which are prohibited under the policy."&lt;SEP&gt;"Receiving more than one payment for the same damage or expense."&lt;SEP&gt;"Receiving multiple payments for the same damage."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-fb0aea7627d6cab63c56603774515efc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9d1b4fcafc6c7d7efe5c322ad9bd33fd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-798fdf9e8255810d437349cea720f315&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cfb324337b8eb7e557e96d41d0a59527</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;ADDITIONAL CHARGES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"Additional charges may be incurred and are the responsibility of the policyholder."&lt;SEP&gt;"Extra costs incurred when a disabled vehicle is towed beyond the nearest qualified repair facility."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-708cd65887876aa076b711ced7a4979e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9cd680372852b670779cd9ab038f278e</data>
