  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"The loss of personal or household services due to bodily injury or death, which is covered under the 'each person' limit."&lt;SEP&gt;"The loss of practical assistance or support from an injured person."</data>
