</node>
<node id="&quot;NON-OWNED AUTO&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"OBJECT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"A non-owned auto being maintained or used during employment in an auto business is excluded."&lt;SEP&gt;"A non-owned auto is a vehicle not owned by the insured but covered under the policy."&lt;SEP&gt;"A non-owned auto is a vehicle not owned by the insured, and its theft may result in loss of use damages."&lt;SEP&gt;"A non-owned auto is a vehicle not owned by the policyholder but covered under the policy, typically used for business or personal purposes."&lt;SEP&gt;"A non-owned auto is a vehicle not owned by, furnished to, or available for regular use by the policyholder, a relative, or a rated resident, and is being operated with the permission of the owner or lawful possessor."&lt;SEP&gt;"A non-owned auto is included in comprehensive coverage."&lt;SEP&gt;"A non-owned auto is subject to the limit of liability."&lt;SEP&gt;"A vehicle not owned by the policyholder and not regularly available for their use, but may still be covered under certain conditions."&lt;SEP&gt;"A vehicle not owned by the policyholder but covered under the policy, typically subject to excess coverage."&lt;SEP&gt;"A vehicle not owned by the policyholder but used occasionally, which may still be covered under the policy."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-245fa605e8e023a6acdcf8c36c35930e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8a3491a1885e53367b27b22e975a6fbb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-708cd65887876aa076b711ced7a4979e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ed4d5b68d5d2c5cb43c341277461c05d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-33661b5c04aa1251a71c27b799dfbfc2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ba971e62cee92a6aaf201ec7e51cf087</data>
</node>
