  <data key="d2">chunk-8a3491a1885e53367b27b22e975a6fbb</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;CUSTOM PARTS OR EQUIPMENT&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"OBJECT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"Aftermarket modifications to a vehicle that are permanently installed and alter its appearance or performance, not included in the original manufacturer’s package."&lt;SEP&gt;"Custom parts or equipment are covered under comprehensive coverage."&lt;SEP&gt;"Custom parts or equipment are modifications or additions to a vehicle that are covered under the policy."&lt;SEP&gt;"Custom parts or equipment are subject to a $1,000 loss limit unless Additional Custom Parts or Equipment Coverage (ACPE) is purchased. If ACPE is purchased, the maximum payment is $1,000 plus the amount of ACPE purchased."&lt;SEP&gt;"Specialized modifications or accessories installed on a covered auto, which are eligible for coverage if purchased."&lt;SEP&gt;"The maximum payment for loss to custom parts or equipment is $1,000 unless ACPE is purchased."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-8a3491a1885e53367b27b22e975a6fbb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9ac858e839dd324c4b80701da2b87bd7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ed4d5b68d5d2c5cb43c341277461c05d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-33661b5c04aa1251a71c27b799dfbfc2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ba971e62cee92a6aaf201ec7e51cf087</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;VANS WITH CABS SEPARATE FROM CARGO AREA&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"VEHICLE TYPE"</data>
  <data key="d4">"Vans with cabs separate from the cargo area are excluded from the definition of 'auto'."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-3bb98005a1307a094baa1b3869aeea6c</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;MULTIPLE AUTO POLICIES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"INSURANCE_POLICY"</data>
  <data key="d4">"Two or more auto insurance policies issued by the same insurer for the same individual, which may affect coverage limits."&lt;SEP&gt;"When more than one auto insurance policy is active for the same individual, the insurer will only pay up to the highest limit available under any single policy."&lt;SEP&gt;"When multiple auto policies are issued by the same insurer, the highest limit of liability for Medical Payments Coverage applies, and no higher payment is made."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-fb0aea7627d6cab63c56603774515efc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9d1b4fcafc6c7d7efe5c322ad9bd33fd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-798fdf9e8255810d437349cea720f315</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;SUSTAINS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"ACTION"</data>
  <data key="d4">"To experience or suffer damage or failure, such as a breakdown."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-708cd65887876aa076b711ced7a4979e</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;WRONGFUL DEATH&quot;">
  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d4">"A legal claim arising from a death caused by negligence."&lt;SEP&gt;"The death of a person due to another’s negligence or wrongful act, which is covered under the 'each person' limit."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-9fee7a00b84094770f04dcfe86a29e3a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cfb324337b8eb7e557e96d41d0a59527</data>
