  <data key="d0">entity</data>
  <data key="d3">"ACTION"</data>
  <data key="d4">"A revolution, or a violent overthrow of a government, is excluded from coverage under the policy."&lt;SEP&gt;"Revolution causes vehicle damage and is excluded."</data>
