<edge source="&lt;hyperedge&gt;&quot;Coverage under this Part II will not apply to bodily injury: 1. sustained by any person while occupying a covered auto while it is being used: a. to carry persons or property for compensation or a fee; b. for retail or wholesale delivery, including, but not limited to, the pickup, transport or delivery of magazines, newspapers, mail or food; or c. for ride-sharing activity.&quot;" target="&quot;BODILY INJURY&quot;">
